@node history "cha_stanley.guide/History"

v2.4 (1999.12.17)
	- save and load marker info (still experimental)
	- now uses OSS instrument numbering

v2.3	minor internal changes, not released

v2.2	third public release

	1999.09.16
		- minor changes for source code sharing
		- arexx put inline for clarity
		- fixed oss_update(), now notify is much quicker
		- fixed default pitch; uses C-3 instead of -|- if not
		  specified

v2.1	second public release

	1999.06.19
		- improved error messages
		- added "working..." status message, now you know when
		  it is finished
		- improved hires mode (before it always selected the
		  timing pulse before the marker, now it chooses the
		  one after if the marker is close to it)

v2.0	not released

	1999.06.17
		- can generate note data


v1.0	first public release

	1999.05.27
		- installs names, and copies finetune etc

	1999.05.25
		- everything works

	1999.05.18
		- can set markers, but not much else

@endnode

